    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of large deciduous, coniferous larch tree reaching 30-60 m talll, native to the mountains of western North America, from British Columbia and Alberta, Canada, to Washington, Oregon, Idaho, and Montana in the U.S.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
